Import Fonts

=============================

1. https://fonts.google.com/

download Poppins

2. edit yaml :

flutter:
  fonts:
    - family: MyCustomFont
      fonts:
        - asset: assets/fonts/MyFont.ttf
        # - asset: assets/fonts/MyFontBold.ttf
        #   weight: 700

3. simple code : 

Text(
  'This is some text in my custom font',
  style: TextStyle(
    fontFamily: 'MyCustomFont',
    fontSize: 18.0,
  ),
),


============================================
